&gt; &gt; &quot;Budoshoshinshu&quot; are really great.  &quot;Musui&#39;s Story - the Autobiogaphy of
a
&gt; &gt; Tokugawa Samurai by Katsu Kokichi is absolutely marvellous as a journal
of
&gt; &gt; the first half of the nineteenth century.
